{"tid":1189591,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益]去飲酒識左個大陸女仔","createTime":"2019-06-07T00:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T02:44:04.000Z","uid":257518,"like":4,"dislike":117,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"75cccef93cc05a0af07c8a1ab9d80dd9d7f71aaa","tid":1189591,"uid":257518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T00:41:14.000Z","msg":"話說有次同同事返大陸飲酒唱K <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就搵左幾個囡囡陪坐<br />\n咁我一直都好少上去呢d地方 算係去應酬同事<br />\n之後坐左陣 媽咪就帶d囡囡入黎<br />\n咁我諗住冇咩所謂啦 都係飲下酒 玩下骰仔<br />\n之後個媽咪同我講<br />\n話陪我坐個女仔第一日返工(唔知有咩意思)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於本人普通話太爛  同性格有d毒<br />\n所以同佢冇咩溝通 有d老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過見佢都飲酒同玩大話骰都幾叻<br />\n就算唔係第一日返工 之前應該都係成日飲酒果d黎<br />\n之後玩左半個鐘左右<br />\n佢突然同我講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識講又唔一早講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係太標準但都聽得明 <br />\n咁就開始傾下計咁<br />\n個女仔廿二歲  細細粒 米五左右<br />\n望落都幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搞到我紅都臉哂<br />\n之後開始熟少少 就緊係攬下玩下咁<br />\n飲左太約3個鐘左右  都差唔多玩完<br />\n啲同事就話走 <br />\n咁佢就攬住叫我加埋佢wechat先走<br />\n咁就返左香港 <br />\n隔左日之後佢就wechat我....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9e3505b433a2fe3a2bd3dc7af138c2296d93a7","tid":1189591,"uid":238296,"like":124,"dislike":3,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T00:48:42.000Z","msg":"大陸妹 <br />\n屌下可以 <br />\n認真就唔好<br />\n<br />\n記得帶袋"},{"pid":"2f5bd3373105a115f2fbbdd8526f20d5a66dd380","tid":1189591,"uid":108016,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T00:49:38.000Z","msg":"大陸雞<br />\n9成有性病"},{"pid":"f0f3a463cb2ecababce28aac737a94d62a31d904","tid":1189591,"uid":104965,"like":100,"dislike":3,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T00:54:10.000Z","msg":"每日150 人就係咁黎⋯<br />\n<br />\n到佢有身分證就會同你離婚<br />\n<br />\n然後申請曬佢鄉下d 人黎團聚呀⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n之後佢會極快申請到公屋<br />\n<br />\n樓主可能變成人財屋3失<br />\n<br />\n巴打⋯切記⋯勿玩火"},{"pid":"4bfd90b5915ac8a38cc54846caa005ee722b2092","tid":1189591,"uid":257518,"like":2,"dislike":77,"score":-75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T00:56:11.000Z","msg":"我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     個女仔：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以下我翻譯為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：在干嘛？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我在想你 （9up)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：那麼會聊天 在想我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你現在還好嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：很好，在上班 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好 你忙完我們再聊會天<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：暫時不能找你 （我以為佢想搵我飲酒R小費）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：沒有叫你找我 只想和你聊會天<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：如果你覺得打擾你 我以後不發信息打擾你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：那我下班再找你聊天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFeel到佢有少少嬲"},{"pid":"e6f50c787f5eb5e71135047065ecd5c9eee5a660","tid":1189591,"uid":150152,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T01:02:00.000Z","msg":"唔好用碌撚諗野啦 矇撚 真係貪你靚仔貪你型咩 想要落黎香港咋，你要既你自己上大陸生活，唔好帶啲蝗蟲落黎"},{"pid":"e4fe85430dc6fee53b909e5de392c194add18a16","tid":1189591,"uid":78971,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T01:03:53.000Z","msg":"見證沉船事故"},{